## ğŸ“¦ Deployment Options

### 1. Local Machine

Just run:

```bash
python gardio.py
```

### 2. GitHub Codespaces

Add this to your repository and start a new Codespace.

### 3. Docker Deployment (optional example)

```dockerfile
FROM python:3.10
WORKDIR /app
COPY . .
RUN pip install torch transformers gradio
CMD ["python", "gardio.py"]
```

